# Run fzf with the follow options:
# - Multi-select enabled (Tab)
# - A given height of 50%
# - Reversed layout (top to bottom)
# - Inline finder info
# - Border with rounded corners
# - Custom pointer
# - Custom raw mode gutter column
# - Custom keybinds:
#   - Ctrl+f: Preview page down (forward)
#   - Ctrl+b: Preview page up (backward)
#   - Alt+r: Toggle raw mode for displaying non-matching items
# - Preview window executing the following script: https://github.com/junegunn/fzf/blob/master/bin/fzf-preview.sh
#   - NOTE: Download and place the fzf-preview.sh file in a directory in your $PATH
# - Rounded corners for the preview window border
# - Radiant Gore color scheme

-m
--height 50%
--layout reverse
--info inline
--border rounded
--pointer='->'
--gutter-raw='â–š'
--bind='ctrl-f:preview-page-down,ctrl-b:preview-page-up,alt-r:toggle-raw'
--preview='fzf-preview.sh {}'
--preview-window='border-rounded'
--color='
  fg:#cacace fg+:#ff6685
  bg+:#4b4b53
  hl:#66b2f0 hl+:#66b2f0
  pointer:#ff6685 marker:#ff6685
  spinner:#ff8a5c info:#ff8a5c separator:#ff6685
  prompt:#ff6685 query:#cacace
  border:#cacace preview-border:#ff6685
  preview-label:#cacace
  scrollbar:#cacace preview-scrollbar:#cacace
'
